</P>
<P>
   moral questions.
</P>
<P>
   12. TRAVELING MERCIES, by Anne Lamott. (Pantheon,
</P>
<P>
   $23.) A chronicle of the author's journey toward faith.
</P>
<P>
   13. A WALK IN THE WOODS, by Bill Bryson. (Broadway,
</P>
<P>
   $25.) A journalist finds beauty and humor while hiking
</P>
<P>
   the Appalachian Trail.
</P>
