<P>
   COXNET PERSONAL TECHNOLOGY 0212 -- For some, the arrival of
February _ Black History Month _ used to mean countless hours in
the library searching for information on such figures as Paul
Robeson, Madame C.J. Walker and Bessie Smith. But today, students
and parents have another reference point _ the Internet. (Poole,
Atlanta Journal-Constitution)
