<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-02-15 13:13 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5787 &Cx1f; ttc-z
r l &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-PET-MEDICINE-2TAKES-L     02-15 0922
