<P>
   Sports stories from The New York Times News Service for
 &UR; TUESDAY &LR; , Feb. 16.
</P>
<P>
   BKN-ARATON-COLUMN (New York) _ Sports of The Times column on the
Knicks-Pistons game. By Harvey Araton.
</P>
<P>
   BKN-KNICKS-PISTONS (New York) _ Detroit (3-2), led by Grant
Hill, are in the Garden for a Presidents' Day game against the
Knicks (2-2), 1 p.m. ET start. By Selena Roberts.
</P>
<P>
   BKN-NETS-HEAT (Miami) _ The N.J. Nets at Miami, 8 p.m. ET start.
By Chris Broussard.
</P>
<P>
