   Monday, Feb. 15, 1999      The Hearst News Service will file these stories for Tuesday:   
(``HNS'' appears in all slug lines.)   
<TEXT>
<P>
   CLINTON-MEXICO (Merida, Mexico) _ President Clinton and Mexico's
President Ernesto Zedillo discuss the problem of drug trafficking
as Mexico comes up for its annual report card from the
administration on how well it's cooperating in the war against
