 &QL; 
INTIMACY (Phoenix) - It's ironic that 30 years after the sexual
revolution in America, we know so much more about sex yet so little
about true intimacy. Why is that? And how do we get there from
here? Ralph Earle and Marilyn Murry of Psychological Counseling
Services in Scottsdale work all the time with couples on intimacy
