<HEADLINE>
AMERICAN SCHEDULE HEADING BACK TOWARD NORMAL
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service Clients) 
By DAN REED 
c.1999 Fort Worth Star-Telegram 
<TEXT>
<P>
   FORT WORTH _ American Airlines operated nearly 90 percent of its
scheduled flights on Monday, for the first time since Feb. 7, as
